main_body:
Germany is hereby authorized to grant aid totalling DM 349,2 million to the German coal industry for the 1994 calendar year, as follows:
- aid totalling DM 179,1 million to Ruhrkohle AG to cover exceptional costs;
- aid totalling DM 170,1 million to the companies Ruhrkohle AG, Saarbergwerke AG, Gewerkschaft Auguste Viktoria, Sophia Jacoba GmbH and Preussag to cover exceptional costs.
